Sr. Do.

00:44:20.780 --> 00:44:21.910
Bueno...

00:44:22.480 --> 00:44:23.680
La cosa es...

00:44:25.150 --> 00:44:26.950
Yo... Así que...

00:44:27.950 --> 00:44:29.190
Puedes hablar libremente.

00:44:30.290 --> 00:44:31.460
Bueno...

00:44:31.860 --> 00:44:33.030
Sr. Do.

